<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"></head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f4f7fb;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">

  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f4f7fb;padding:40px 0;">
    <tr><td align="center">
      <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#fff;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08);">

        <!-- Header -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#1a3c5e;padding:32px 40px;text-align:center;">
            <h1 style="margin:0;color:#fff;font-size:24px;font-weight:800;">
              Cabinet <span style="color:#2aa4b5;">Martin</span>
            </h1>
            <p style="margin:6px 0 0;color:#b8cfe0;font-size:13px;">7, rue des Archives — 53 000 Laval</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Bannière -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#2aa4b5;padding:24px;text-align:center;">
            <p style="margin:0;color:#fff;font-size:32px;">📅</p>
            <p style="margin:8px 0 0;color:#fff;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;">Rendez-vous confirmé</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Corps -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:40px;">
            <p style="margin:0 0 16px;color:#2c2c2c;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">
              Bonjour <strong>{{ rdv.patient.personne.prenom }} {{ rdv.patient.personne.nom }}</strong>,
            </p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 28px;color:#2c2c2c;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">
              Votre rendez-vous au Cabinet Martin a bien été enregistré. Voici le récapitulatif :
            </p>

            <!-- Récap RDV -->
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:28px;border-collapse:collapse;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;">
              <tr style="background:#f4f7fb;border-bottom:1px solid #e8edf3;">
                <td style="padding:12px 18px;color:#888;font-size:13px;width:40%;">Date</td>
                <td style="padding:12px 18px;color:#1a3c5e;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;">
                  {{ rdv.dateDebutRDV|date('l d MMMM Y')|capitalize }}
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="background:#fff;border-bottom:1px solid #e8edf3;">
                <td style="padding:12px 18px;color:#888;font-size:13px;">Heure</td>
                <td style="padding:12px 18px;color:#1a3c5e;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;">
                  {{ rdv.dateDebutRDV|date('H:i') }} — {{ rdv.dateFinRDV|date('H:i') }}
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="background:#f4f7fb;border-bottom:1px solid #e8edf3;">
                <td style="padding:12px 18px;color:#888;font-size:13px;">Médecin</td>
                <td style="padding:12px 18px;color:#1a3c5e;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;">
                  Dr #{{ rdv.medecin.id }}{% if rdv.medecin.specMedecin %} — {{ rdv.medecin.specMedecin }}{% endif %}
                </td>
              </tr>
              {% if rdv.commentaireRDV %}
              <tr style="background:#fff;">
                <td style="padding:12px 18px;color:#888;font-size:13px;">Motif</td>
                <td style="padding:12px 18px;color:#2c2c2c;font-size:14px;">{{ rdv.commentaireRDV }}</td>
              </tr>
              {% endif %}
            </table>

            <!-- Adresse -->
            <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#eef4fb;border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;width:100%;margin-bottom:24px;">
              <tr>
                <td style="color:#1a3c5e;font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;">
                  <strong>📍 Cabinet Martin</strong><br>
                  7, rue des Archives<br>
                  53 000 Laval<br>
                  02 99 99 99 99
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>

            <p style="margin:0;color:#999;font-size:12px;">
              Pour annuler ou modifier ce rendez-vous, contactez-nous au <strong>02 99 99 99 99</strong> ou par email.
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#f4f7fb;padding:24px 40px;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid #eee;">
            <p style="margin:0;color:#aaa;font-size:11px;">
              Cabinet Martin &mdash; 02 99 99 99 99 &mdash; cabinetmartinonline535@gmail.com
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>

      </table>
    </td></tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
